Elite House Plans - Creative Plans for Yard and Garden + Live-work Planning and Design - Mantesh

1. Elite House Plans - Michael Lane - 2011 - 

The Elite Book of House Plans provides a variety of house plans and blueprints in different styles including single storey (bungalows) 
dormers and two storey designs. Traditional modern and contemporary houses are presented.

================================

2. Xplans: Book of House Plans - Michael Lane - 2012

The Xplans Book of House Plans provides a variety of house plans and blueprints in different styles including single storey (bungalows) dormers and two storey 
designs. Traditional modern and contemporary houses are presented.

=================================

3. Creative Plans for Yard and Garden Structures: 42 Easy-To-Build Designs for Gazebos, Sheds, Pool Houses, Playsets, Bridges and More! - Connie Brown , Matt Debacker, Inc Home Planners 

This book contains a brief overview of 42 plans of outdoor structures ranging from gazebos to to playhouses to compost bins to swings to bridges.

==================================

4. Live-work Planning and Design : Zero-commute Housing - Thomas Dolan - 2012

Live-Work Planning and Design is the only comprehensive guide to the design and planning of live-work spaces for architects, designers, 
and urban planners. Readers will learn from built examples of live-work, both new construction and renovation, in a variety of locations. Urban planners, 
developers, and economic development staff will learn how various municipalities have developed 
and incorporated live-work within building codes and city plans.

================================
